{"tid":598084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【直線嬲屌】「比基尼航空」開印度航線　網友：太危險","createTime":"2018-03-19T08:15:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T09:12:54.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6ceb994980abc6f00f32eb06b5a6a2d5dbfed8","tid":598084,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T08:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180319/640_28f233f3de59587d3c5b23634fe8f9aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180319%2F640_28f233f3de59587d3c5b23634fe8f9aa.jpg&h=6f775817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180319/640_874223f884375f83ef9487ab15f577ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180319%2F640_874223f884375f83ef9487ab15f577ba.jpg&h=c155cd23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「比基尼航空」之稱的越南廉航越捷航空（VietJet Air）宣布新增直飛印度航線，引起網友譁然，有網友直說：「她們知道印度人如何對待婦女嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n越捷航空宣布將新增將於今年7至8月，新增由胡志明巿直飛新德里的航線，初步預計每周有約4班航班。<br />\n <br />\n越捷航空向來以性感巿場策略見稱，女行政總裁阮氏芳邵（Nguyen Thi Phuong Thao）因聘請泳裝模特兒上航班表演而為越捷打出名堂，她本人更成為越南首位億萬女富翁。越捷曾以一場空中比基尼秀，歡迎在U23亞洲盃勇奪亞軍的越南隊球員，當時讓球員非常尷尬。<br />\n <br />\n如今「比基尼航空」將登陸印度，更令網友譁然，有網友質疑做法太危險，有人直言：「她們知道印度如何對待婦女嗎？印度男人可以強姦一個8個月大的寶寶、18歲女童以至80歲的婆婆，然後還歸咎受害人的衣服。我猜航空公司需要重新考慮一下。」也有網友坦言一旦航班降落印度必定引起混亂。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n <br />\n跟上國際脈動，快來蘋果國際按讚<br />\n<br />\n片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180319/1317424/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180319%2F1317424%2F&d=oK81T%2BzW%2FRBjANvf%2FMit2QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=593db051\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180319%2F1317424%2F&h=35f0a79b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180319/1317424/</a>"},{"pid":"5a759d3678fa601eb521b964ae2aa66959f416dd","tid":598084,"uid":22999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"第一張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}